<p>I found some suggested code at:
<a href="http://www.nabble.com/Re:-Subclassing-Zend_Auth_Adapter_DbTable-suggestion-p10117207s16154.html">http://nabble.com/Re:-Subclassing-Zend_Auth_Adapteâ€¦</a></p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
/**
     * getResultRowObject() - Returns the result row as a stdClass  
object
     *
     * @return stdClass
     */
public function getResultRowObject()
{
     $returnObject = new stdClass();

     foreach ($this-&gt;_resultRow as $resultColumn =&gt; $resultValue) {
         $returnObject-&gt;{$resultColumn} = $resultValue;
     }
     return $returnObject;
} 
